{"tid":2226744,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK 新歌上架不到一小時破千萬瀏覽！全球最強女團力壓川普確診消息","createTime":"2020-10-02T08:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T17:28:24.000Z","uid":16659,"like":47,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"fce5d248f5f6f99a86e28b63176285a9891730f8","tid":2226744,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T08:14:19.000Z","msg":"韓國女團 BLACKPINK 又破紀錄啦！今（2）天台灣時間12點、全球同步上架首張正規專輯最新主打〈Lovesick Girls〉，MV推出短短不到一小時就衝破千萬瀏覽不說，甚至力壓稍早傳出武漢肺炎確診的美國總統川普、拿下Twitter搜尋關鍵字冠軍，堪稱是全球最強女團！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/10/02/201002-14636-10-lc9hu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F10%2F02%2F201002-14636-10-lc9hu.jpg&h=42e3beb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBLACKPINK 堪稱是目前全球最強女團！（翻攝自blackpinkofficial IG）<br />\n2020年可謂是 BLACKPINK 的大躍進年，不只狂掃亞洲，進軍國際更是頻頻拿下好成績，先是與國際大咖Lady Gaga、賽琳娜（Selena Gomez）接連攜手合作，就連 Netflix也看上她們的高人氣拍攝專屬音樂紀錄片。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/10/02/201002-14636-2-4tSjd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F10%2F02%2F201002-14636-2-4tSjd.jpg&h=41128690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBLACKPINK 新歌上架不到一小時破千萬瀏覽！（翻攝自youtube）<br />\n今天台灣時間中午12點，首張正規專輯《The Album》首波主打〈Lovesick Girls〉全球同步推出，果然一舉又破紀錄，短短不到一小時就衝破千萬瀏覽次數，甚至在Twitter搜尋關鍵字中，還力壓稍早傳出武漢肺炎確診的美國總統川普，魅力無法擋！"},{"pid":"292d3d2152a789c72a73f3f5049b07a7f7494ecc","tid":2226744,"uid":303133,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T08:15:21.000Z","msg":"Jisoo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b049e67eae702afca7a4bd4d9d3ce38cb0ccdc43","tid":2226744,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T08:15:23.000Z","msg":"包皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7526e42fa297ea7faf003f3745613e